sentences: Stefanie Ann Sargent (June 1, 1968 – June 27, 1992) was an American musician.
She was the lead guitarist and co-founder of Seattle punk rock band 7 Year Bitch.
Sargent was born to Paula and Kenneth Sargent on June 1, 1968, in Seattle, Washington, where she was raised.
She had been a member of several bands by 1990, when she co-founded 7 Year Bitch alongside Selene Vigil, Valerie Agnew and Elizabeth Davis.
